description:
In this karaoke / instrumental hymn, we'll explore the lyrics and melody of When peace, like a river. This peaceful song is perfect for a church service or special occasion, and can be sung either solo or in a choir. If you're looking for a worship song to sung at a special occasion, this is the perfect choice!

First Line: When peace, like a river, attendeth my way
Title: When Peace, Like a River
Author: Horatio Gates Spafford (1873)
Music performed by Mr. C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters' karaoke youtube
